data.description: Upgrade your living experience with the Schuber Mitchell Sydney floor plan. This stunnng home comes packed with top-of-the-line features that will make you fall in love at first sight. Enjoy the luxury f custom window treatments, a smart home package, and a whole house water filtration system with reverse osmosis for pure, clean water. Never run out of hot water again with the 80-gallon hot water tank, and cook like a pro with the Frigidaire appliance package in your spacious kitchen complete with a pantry and ample storage. Rest easy knowing you're prepared for any storm with included 22k Generac generator and Atlas storm shelter. The full brick exterior and insulated 3-car garage offer both durability and convenience. And when it's time to relax, step into your privacy fenced back yard with an extended patio. Upgrade your lifestyle today with this incredible home.
